'Origin Point' = Center of Mass = In blender - when you 'Bend' it bends it according to the origin point - which also affects rotation / physics 
  'Set Origin' = select objects -> 'Right Click' -> 'Set Origin' -> 'Origin to Geometry'
'Outline' = Top right box that contains every object we've created - to organise : group things together by creating 'Collections' button in top right corner
  'Move' Objects in a collection = Press 'M' With Objects you want to move selected / Click and drag items from outline
