'Shift + `' (tilda)(with camera selected) = Fly Mode = 'View' Dropdown -> 'Navigation' -> 'Fly Navigation' = Allows you to move with 'WASD E(up)Q(down)' controls FPV - very sensitive controls - 'Scroll Wheel' to change sensitivty
  'Fly Mode' Also works without camera, any time you want to move with 'WASD QE' just use 'Shift + `' (tilda)
'Properties' -> 'Scene' -> 'Render' -> 'Render Engine' = You can change which engine you use to render
  Tut (13:30)- Above Properties -> 'Shadows' -> 'Cube Size' = 4096px / 
